"5:120:11" : {s: 5, a: 120, w: 11, r: "قدر", t: "قَدِيرٌۢ", l: "قَدِير", lc: 45, tl: "qadīrun", lb: "মহাক্ষমতাবান, পরিপূর্ণ সক্ষম/ সর্বশক্তিমান (القَدِيْر)",e: "All-Powerful", b: "সর্বশক্তিমান", i: "Maha Kuasa", f: 37, rm: "to measure/decree/determine/stint/straiten, to have power, to be able, a measure, means, ability, a term/decree, doom, destiny, measured, decreed."},
